summary: Help a desperate noble solve an urgent fashion crisis.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=6]FREDAS NIGHT FASHION[/size]
[size=5]
[/size][size=5]A fully voiced quest mod! [/size]

[size=3]This quest is started in the city of Solitude. Inside The Winking
Skeever Inn, the player can find Helen. She desperately needs a new
fur coat for Fredas night dinner, and will pay the player to track down her missing fur
trader.[/size]

[size=4]
Check out a teaser [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iILxhSckryE]here[/url]!
[/size]
[youtube]iILxhSckryE[/youtube]

[size=5]Compatibility: [/size]

[size=3]Full compatability with all of Skyrim's DLCs. Small changes have been made to the tamriel world space, so I cannot guarantee compatibility with other mods. [/size]

[size=5]Length:[/size]

[size=3]This quest adds approximately 20 minutes of gameplay, with 2 uniquely and fully voiced NPCs, and a new cave. [/size]

[size=5]Contributors:[/size]

[size=3]Special thanks to mskrysdescending for voicing Helen and brendaniel for voicing Jedd![/size]

[size=5]Contact:[/size]

[size=3]Please contact me via the comments section or alternatively at collinjosephanthony@gmail.com if you have any questions.[/size][/center]
author: Collin Anthony or DoubtSuspended
